<p>Hey there!</p>

<p>I'm <a href="https://andycroll.com">Andy</a> from <a href="https://firstrubyfriend.org">First #RubyFriend</a>, a volunteer effort to get new folks to meet experienced Ruby programmers.</p> 

<p>You (hopefully within the last month or so if I'm doing this right) signed up to find a mentor from the Ruby community to help you find your feet in your software engineering career.</p>

